aston.group20.model

Class LightAircraft

  • java.lang.Object
    • aston.group20.model.Aircraft
      • aston.group20.model.PoweredAircraft
        • aston.group20.model.LightAircraft
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAircraft, java.lang.Comparable<IAircraft>

    public class LightAircraft
extends PoweredAircraft
    This concrete subclass defines the characteristics of LightAircraft; it defines the landing time, the takeoff time and the length of time it can fly for (it's fuel level) in order to successfully inherit from the PoweredAircraft class.
    Version:
    1.0, March 2014
    Author:
    Group_20
